WEBVTT

00:04:58.045 --> 00:05:02.606
when they had me
chained by the neck to a tree.

00:05:03.947 --> 00:05:07.234
They kept me outside that day,

00:05:08.266 --> 00:05:10.001
during a tropical downpour.

00:05:11.238 --> 00:05:16.538
I remember feeling an urgent need
to use the bathroom.

00:05:21.012 --> 00:05:22.549
"Whatever you have to do,

00:05:24.796 --> 00:05:26.796
you'll do in front of me,